{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_01","textHome":"欸~？你想知道我的名字~？…既然来问我的@名字，那你当然会替我保守住秘密的吧~？@那么，告诉你或许也没关系。…我是笠音青@，是PROMISED BLOOD的三女@~。要是你把这泄露给神滨的魔法少女了的@话…我可不会饶过你的哦~？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_17","textHome":"帮派呀公会呀，这些需要交流能力的游戏我不@是很适应呢~。毕竟去和他人搭话、交朋友@也很累…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_18","textHome":"我现在沉迷的网络游戏，即便一个人玩也能享@受~。游戏里的玩家形象很有设计感，可以@说有一种我的分身的感觉哦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_19","textHome":"哇哦~，必杀技更容易积攒了~！太好啦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_20","textHome":"我已经做好了和神滨那帮人战斗的决心。为了@让二木不再发生争斗…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_21","textHome":"我刚成为魔法少女的时候，可没有什么目标可@言…。不过呢，现在是的的确确地有的。我@想让二木的魔法少女，脸上都重新挂上笑容@…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_22","textHome":"我会让神滨那帮人偿还她们的罪行的…。然后@把系统带回二木，帮助同伴们…。虽然我一@个人是做不到的，但有姐姐大人和姐姐在的@话绝对可以…！就算，最终血流成河…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_23","textHome":"不论通过争斗拿到了什么，都只会催生别的争@斗的火种…。只要没有压倒性的强大，就不@可能完全停止掉争斗…。所以，我想变强。@我会不输给任何人，飞越自己的极限…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_24","textHome":"嗯~？啊，你来了啊。辛苦了~。要不要拿点@喝的出来呢~？现在有…汽水或者橙汁！你@要哪个~？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_25","textHome":"唔~…早上好~…。早上真是难受啊~…。玩@着游戏读着漫画就染上了熬夜的习惯…哈、@哈啊、啊…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":102300,"motion":400,"tear":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_26","textHome":"午饭怎么办呢~。在据点的时候小光会做给我@们吃，不用考虑，很轻松…嗯~，没办法了@。去买点什么吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_02","textHome":"我是笠音青~。我呢，其实还挺强的，所以可@以把我当作依靠哦~？相应地，我也会收取@报酬，还请多关照啦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_27","textHome":"我的学校没有归宅部，必须加入某项社团活动@才行~。而且每个月必须出席一次…哈啊，@真没劲啊~，茶道部…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_28","textHome":"啊，已经这个时间了？我现在玩的游戏，有一@个只有这个点才会出现的boss~。三下@五除二把boss打掉，拿稀有掉落去咯~@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_29","textHome":"作业的话我已经做了哦~。因为不想被催促，@所以每日任务总之是全部完成的哦~。哼哼@，是不是对我有点改观了？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_30","textHome":"准备还OK吗~？虽然我觉得应该没问题…但@碰上危险就按各自的判断逃走吧~。…那么@，行动开始！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界吗…这种像是游戏的副本一样的地点@竟然真的实际存在，神滨可真是个奇怪的地@方~。…嗯，也许有去攻略的价值？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_32","textHome":"集团战吗…虽然不是很乐意，但避免不了也无@可奈何呢…。…好了，听从我的指示。为了@不再失去任何人，我会加油的…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_33","textHome":"怎么样才能变得敢触碰活的生物呢~？看着照@片和影像的时候倒是感觉没事~…。…真想@哪天能够摸一下仓鼠啊~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_34","textHome":"闲着也是闲着，要不要去漫画咖啡店呢~。你@读漫画之类的吗？…啊，我不是在邀请你。@我只是想着，要是你有推荐的话，就听听看@好了~而已"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_35","textHome":"在家里，爸妈成天唠叨我快去学习真的很烦，@所以最近到姐姐大人家里避难了~。也可以@玩游戏，真是帮大忙了~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_36","textHome":"可以玩桌游的咖啡厅吗~。虽然挺想去尝试一@下的，但要和不认识的人一起玩，实在也不@太能接受…。…像小光的话，会愿意陪我去@吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_03","textHome":"要是那个时候，我身边拥有朋友的话，或许未@来就不一样了~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_37","textHome":"兰华和朔夜在潜入神滨的行动中，应该不会出@岔子~。也不是说不担心，只是她们的经验@值可是比我要获得的多的呀~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_38","textHome":"姐姐可真是过分啊~！VR套装，买来的当天@就给破坏掉了~！哦，在生气的可不只是我@啊!?姐姐大人也给惊呆了…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":400}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_39","textHome":"草、草、草莓~！这个，试姐姐大人送来的慰@问品吗!?太好了，这些绝对很好吃的~！@那么，我开吃啦~！…嗯~，好吃~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_40","textHome":"我呢，没有朋友的~。毕竟我也一直以来喜欢@一个人玩。二木的大家也不是朋友哦。…不@过…大概算是，同伴。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1023_00_41","textHome":"这个冰糕，要吃吗~？啊——，张嘴~！…哼@哼，吃到了吧…？这个，其实是姐姐大人的@~。擅自吃掉，可能会被她发火的哦~。欸@嘿"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":102300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102300}